# Path C Slice 2: clear ALL world collision objects (and attached objects) from
# move_group's planning scene. Enumerates current ids via /get_planning_scene
# then REMOVEs each via an /apply_planning_scene diff. Requires confirm==true.
#
# --- request ---
bool    confirm                      # must be true to act (cheap guard)
---
# --- response ---
bool    success
int32   removed_count                # number of objects removed (finite, never NaN)
string  error_message                # human-readable on failure
